  fig <- fig %>% add_trace(y = ~yhat, name = 'Trend', mode = 'lines', fill = "tonexty",

  fig <- fig %>% add_trace(y = ~Price, name = 'Price', mode = 'lines',line=list(color=c('green'),dash = "solid"))

  amin = min(a,b,c) *.90
  brange = as.numeric(max(data$Date) - min(data$Date))

  fig = fig %>% layout(annotations = list(text = paste0(format(a,"<b>%b %d, %Y"),"—"),  x = Sys.Date()-brange, y = amax * .95 ,showarrow=FALSE ),
                       shapes = list(list(type = "rect", text = 'decline1', fillcolor = "white", line = list(color = "green"),
                                          opacity = 0.1, y0 = 0.6, y1 = amax, x0 = Sys.Date(), x1 = Sys.Date() + 365),
                                     vline(as.Date(Sys.Date()),text)))
  
  Noax <- list(title = "", zeroline = FALSE,
               showline = FALSE, showticklabels = TRUE,
               side = "right", showgrid = TRUE, fixedrange = F,
